main event: A witness observed a UFO with 4 lights (1 red and 3 white) that appeared to maneuver and was brighter than a light bulb in Cincinnati, Ohio on May 6, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared to have 4 lights, one red and 3 white, and was brighter than a light bulb.
The object appeared to maneuver 2-3 times in diameter.
The witness was outside at night in West Terrace, Cincinnati, Ohio when they observed the object for about 10 minutes.
The witness described the object as having a solid appearance and changing brightness.
The witness provided a sketch showing the object's motion and position in the sky.
sighted object: A UFO with 4 lights (1 red, 3 white)
